reviews_data.review_text: Super cute place, good coffee.

I found this place during a Google search, and it turned out to be a pleasant surprise. Anyone who hosts meetings knows the value of a great coffee shop. I stopped by today to explore, and I’m so glad I did.

While I didn’t order food, I did enjoy a refreshing pistachio tea. Even more enjoyable was my conversation with Mattie. She is an entrepreneur with a spirit-filled mission, and her polite and welcoming nature makes this a comfortable space to visit or work within. I love that she truly understands the meaning of service in customer service.

May God send you a multitude of blessings.
Humbly,
Great coffee, pastries were delicious. Love the decor/atmosphere of the cafe. The prices were also really reasonable. Wish I lived closer!

My new go-to coffee spot! The owner is very sweet and the atmosphere is amazing. Coffee is some of the best (I also love the matcha). A great place to relax and even work on your laptop if needed. Pastries are also delicious!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Margo, 
Thank you for your kind review! We are honored that you choose us to work from and love your company :)

reviews_data.review_text: Super cute coffee shop with nice seating areas - can study or just sit around and talk. The drinks were good and there were some fun seasonal options too. Outdoor Adirondacks were inviting as well for a nice day.
Adorable little place. The atmosphere is very " coffee house" rustic.

One of my favorite coffee shops in the area! Great coffee, fast and friendly service, incredible atmosphere, and awesome customer service. The space is roomy and clean, all around awesome experience! I definitely recommend!
Coffee was great, got an iced chai. The decor and service were really nice. Good vibes and relaxing — will definitely return :)
Good soup
Love the cozy atmosphere. My whole family went to spend some quality time together.   My Chi Latte was fab!
A diamond in the rough when it comes to coffee shops in Concord. Inside is absolutely stunning, coffee is wonderful, WiFi is strong..what more can you ask for? Will definitely come back ❤️

review_questions.Seating type: Indoor dining area, Outdoor patio / terrace

reviews_data.owner_answer:
Carlos, 

We are so glad and honored you enjoyed our space! We hope to see you soon <3

reviews_data.review_text: This new coffee shop is an absolute gem! The coffee is amazing—rich, flavorful, and expertly made. The customer service is top-notch, with a friendly and welcoming staff that makes you feel right at home. On top of that, the space is beautifully designed, creating the perfect atmosphere to relax, work, or catch up with friends. Whether you’re a coffee lover or just looking for a great spot to unwind, this place is a must-visit. Highly recommend!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Gigi, 
We appreciate your kind review! It means the world to us and we are honored that you have enjoyed the space and coffee. <3

reviews_data.review_text: Love the vibes! The staff is super friendly and the atmosphere is very unique. Got the cherry van coke with espresso and its wonderful

It’s difficult to find a place with a unique but inviting atmosphere, inspired coffee/tea offerings, and fitting pastries that pair well, but Mattie Ruth’s executes on all three. It’s a relaxing spot to read and enjoy a treat.

Lovely coffee shop with delicious coffees and pastries. There are many cozy spots to sit and chat, even outdoor seating over looking Gibson Mill. The owner is very friendly and nice to talk to. Very fair prices, as well. The drip coffee is 10 out of 10!
The Best coffee in town

Quaint cottage-core cafe ☕️ Best coffee shop in Concord!  I’ve been to every cafe in town this one ranks #1.  Perfect latte. Even my father was impressed by his Americano and ordered a second one. I highly recommend you stop in.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Jonathan, 
First off that photo is amazing :)
Secondly, we really appreciate your kind review. We are honored and hope to see you back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Been here a few times now!! The owner is super sweet and friendly. She let me bring my dog in 🥺❤️. There are cute couches, tables and chairs along with books and games. The decorations are unique and beautiful. Their lattes are amazing and they make it pretty fast! Beautiful atmosphere I 100% recommend coming here!
Lovely people, vibe. Delicious coffee and eats.

I absolutely love the coffee and atmosphere here! Their mocha is my favorite, and I enjoy it daily. The owner is incredibly friendly, and the peaceful environment creates a wonderful sense of community. It’s truly the best!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Sai, 
Thank you for your review <3
You are one of our favorite regulars and we appreciate your constant support, it means so much!

reviews_data.review_text: Excellent coffee shop with unique character. A local gem. Delicious coffee and pastries ☕️🥐
Cute little coffee shop with nice baristas and atmosphere. Only thing is they don’t do decaf espresso but do have decaf drip.
Love it🤎
Beautiful coffee shop! ♥️ Coffee’s great and the atmosphere comfortable. Service is top tier as well!!
Great vibes all around. The espresso beans to go are a hit!
Truly unique experience in Gibson area.

This is such a refreshing, relaxing and cozy spot!!! The coffee is AMAZING & the delectables they offer are exquisite!!! I always get a Cortado with oat milk (which I call liquid velvet bc it’s so smooth!). The cinnamon roll & the chicken salad are phenomenal 🤌🏾 The owner and the barista’s are so friendly and pleasant!  I HIGHLY recommend this place!!!
Very sweet staff. The Matcha latte is very cozy. Love the atmosphere. There’s not gluten free pastry options, but it seemed they had an option or two in the fridge like chicken salad.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Jess, 
We are so glad you enjoyed your time at the shop! Thanks for stopping in, we hope to see you again soon.

reviews_data.review_text: Amazing coffee shop in the heart of Concord!
Great peaceful vibe with comfortable seating inside and out.  Very friendly, solid coffee.

We have so needed something like this in this area! It is something pulled right out of a Pinterest page.

The prices are very reasonable, the atmosphere inviting, and the owner and her mom super pleasant. This is going to be a new favorite!!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Thank you for stoping by, we are glad you enjoyed it!
Come see us again soon :)

reviews_data.review_text: Great atmosphere, good vibe and great coffee.   My new favorite

Obsessed. The service is wonderful and the vibes are immaculate. Vintage accents, cowhide and turkish rugs, pale pink and lots of art. I feel so at home. Best coffee shop in Cabarrus County! Their flat white is also a must try and perfection.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Danielle,
We appreciate your kind review! 
We hop you come back and see us soon.

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee and atmosphere, such a cool little spot! We have been here 4 times now and it’s never disappointed
Our new favorite spot! Best latte around and the service is great! Welcome to the neighborhood!
Our new favorite coffee shop. Coffee and pastries are amazing and the shop is so cozy and inviting. Service is amazing as well, almost like going to a family member’s home for coffee!
